quote.summary: Ubtech Robotics Corp Ltd is a China-based company primarily engaged in the design, production, commercialization, and sales of smart service robotic products and solutions. The Company operates four segments. Education Smart Robotic Products and Services segment is engaged in providing smart robotic products including humanoid Yanshee, Alpha Mini and uKit and Jimu series. Logistics Smart Robotic Products and Services segment is engaged in providing automated guided vehicles (AGVs) and automated mobile robots (AMRs) under Wali series. Other Sector-Tailored Smart Robotic Products and Services segment is engaged in providing smart robotic products and services covering various use scenarios including schools, hospitals, airports, and train stations, among others. Consumer-Level Robots and Other Hardware Devices segment is engaged in the sales of robotic products with artificial intelligence (AI)-functions, including AiRROBO vacuum cleaner and AiRROBO cat litter box and Alpha Mini series.
